_:N72d1bb2031d34edda49e8d1881d66bc5 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Sir Alan Campbell was appointed Lord President of the Council, and Leader of the House of Commons on 5 September 2025. He was previously Parliamentary Secretary to the Treasury (Chief Whip) between 5 July 2024 and 5 September 2025. He was elected as the MP for Tynemouth in May 1997.</p>\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
